WEBVTT


00:00:00.251 --> 00:00:01.674
If you are a migrant, 

00:00:01.674 --> 00:00:03.874
listen because this interests you.

00:00:03.891 --> 00:00:06.081
The government has just informed

00:00:06.491 --> 00:00:08.642
that at the beginning of 2024

00:00:08.642 --> 00:00:10.936
the immigration regulations will be reformed

00:00:10.936 --> 00:00:13.152
to simplify procedures and to inflate

00:00:13.152 --> 00:00:14.394
and improve protection

00:00:14.411 --> 00:00:16.254
of migrants' rights.

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.742
Incorporating 1 Community directive,

00:00:18.742 --> 00:00:20.802
you can request 1 residence,

00:00:20.802 --> 00:00:22.592
1 residence and work permit

00:00:22.592 --> 00:00:25.551
within a maximum period of 90 days.

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:26.717
Therefore, 

00:00:26.717 --> 00:00:28.920
equal treatment will be ensured.

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:29.990
among migrants

00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:30.700
requesting

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:32.719
this residence and work permit

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.479
with eh the Spaniards

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:37.959
and are to be protected against labor exploitation.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:38.679
Therefore, 

00:00:38.679 --> 00:00:40.349
what will be guaranteed are

00:00:40.349 --> 00:00:41.370
the guarantees of protection

00:00:41.370 --> 00:00:42.579
against labor exploitation,

00:00:42.950 --> 00:00:44.827
the improvement of residents' rights

00:00:44.827 --> 00:00:45.627
long-lasting

00:00:45.670 --> 00:00:47.017
and their families.

00:00:47.270 --> 00:00:50.417
What did you think of this 2024 reform?

00:00:50.417 --> 00:00:51.577
of the law on foreigners?

00:00:51.690 --> 00:00:52.877
Leave it in the comments!
